node.text: Today was my students’ last day of school! It has been a hectic past few weeks trying to help several of them get caught up with assignments! 😬 Teachers are done next Tuesday and then I can fully relax and enjoy my summer! 🙌🏼 Just thought I’d share some close-up views of my dining room with you this evening. I’ve linked all I can, including my mirrored buffet, chandelier, and gray velvet runner on my LIKEtoKNOW.it page. Download the app for free to shop my home. 💗 Have a wonderful night! #diningroominspo #diningroomideas #diningroomdecor #diningroomtable #diyprojects #diydiningtable #diningtabledecor #homedecor #interiordesigninspo #interiordesign

node.text: Happy Tuesday IG friends! It was time to finally replace my very old, worn-out mattress and I was so happy when I heard that Lull wanted to partner with me in making this possible! #sponsored  I am sharing the very convenient process with all of you, from receiving my new Lull mattress at my doorstep to unboxing it and getting it all set up on my bed.  Buying a new mattress has never been easier and shipping is always free! In addition, Lull allows a 100 night trial period and if you're not totally satisfied within that time frame, returns are free too! 🙌🏼 The three layer technology with a gel-infused memory foam top layer contours to your body and pulls away heat, making it so comfortable without the sinking-in feeling. We have had the pleasure to try it out now for 5 nights and we love it so far!  My husband is already saying his back feels better and please note that Lull is not paying me to say that. 😊 I look forward to many more restful nights on my new Lull mattress! Get $150 off today at https://lull.com/designsbyjeana
After several requests, I’m giving you a full look inside every room in my home!! 🙌🏼 Hope you enjoy! 😊#housetour #myhome #interiorinspiration #hometour #homedecor

For now, you can swipe left to see Chip’s new favorite spot to chill 🐶 as well as how our little porch looked when we started. I got so many questions about the door when I shared it in my stories.  It was custom built by David @ironsharpensiron100.  So glad I found him! His work is amazing! 😍 Have a beautiful day! ❤️

node.text:
New backsplash versus the old one (swipe left). When I added this Mother of Pearl peel-and-stick backsplash back in January, a lot of strong opinions were shared. 😆 My main goals were to A) brighten up this space and B) find something pretty that was easy enough for me to apply. When I stumbled across this gorgeous, shimmering peel-and-stick backsplash, I knew I’d achieve both of those goals. 🤗 Which one is your favorite? No right or wrong answer (just please don’t be too harsh 😜). I have all the info and link to the backsplash on my blog. Have a beautiful Tuesday! 💕

Well, here it is! #sponsored  thanks to #walmarthome I finally organized my linen closet and I’m so happy with how it turned out! 😆 (Swipe to see the before.) Since traveling and hosting are back again, I decided to change things up and turned this space into a guest room closet. All the guest essentials organized in one place are sure to make anyone feel welcomed! 🤗 I have more details about what I did in this space as well as info about Walmart’s new Wow and Now section (where I found my cute baskets) on my blog - link in bio. 
:
Have a beautiful start to your weekend! 😘
